README

WIN BLACKJACK

Fact: gambling is fun. Fact: winning is the best part of gambling.
Fact: this app will train you to win blackjack as much as possible.

What this app does:
Shows a hand, including what cards you hold and what card the dealer
shows. You then select hit, stand, double, or split. The app informs
you if you were correct, and if not, informs you what the optimal
move was. 

What this app does not do:
Teach you how to count cards.

What this app will do in the future:
//When all the features in this category are included, 
//I will consider the app ready for release on the 
//Google Play store, free of charge and without ads.
1. Allow a user to look up the optimal move given any hand.